Welcome home to 271 Shipley, an urban dweller's sanctuary, located in the heart of vibrant SOMA yet tucked away on a slower-paced street. This sleek town-home-like condo is drenched in natural sunlight and boasts 3 levels of private and functional living spaces. Tastefully updated, this home boasts vaulted ceilings, skylights, big windows, impressive hardwood floors, and high-quality finishes. Designed for entertaining, the main living level includes an open concept floor plan, and private deck perfect for your morning coffee ritual. Enjoy intimate home-cooked meals with loved ones, and indulge in a glass of wine with friends in front of your modern, wood-burning fireplace on a crisp San Francisco evening. The modern, utilitarian chef's kitchen makes cooking fun and is complete with chic appliances, sleek quartz countertops, and ample cabinet space.
